    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigators are examining the quality improvement impact of providing patients with a an
      electronic health record-connected blood pressure cuff. Investigators will give half of
      patients already eligible for hypertension management within a clinical pharmacist panel, the
      ability to upload their blood pressure data into Stanford's electronic health record.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
